Flag runtests
  Description: Build and run tests
  
Executable test
  Path: test
  MainIs: test.ml
  Install: false
  Build$: flag(runtests)
  BuildDepends: batteries, fstar, fstar.evp, fstar.db
  CompiledObject: native
  
Test main
  Run$: flag(runtests)
  Command: $test
